{
  "ComponentID": "HMC5883L",
  "ComponentType": "3-Axis Digital Magnetometer / Compass IC",
  "Description": "The HMC5883L is a low-power, surface-mount, multi-chip module integrating three anisotropic magnetoresistive (AMR) sensors and a dedicated ASIC. It provides digital 3-axis magnetic field sensing for applications like electronic compassing. The ASIC handles signal amplification, automatic degaussing (set/reset), offset cancellation, and includes a 12-bit ADC. Data is output via an I²C serial interface, enabling heading accuracy of 1° to 2°. It is designed for low-voltage operation in consumer and navigation devices.",
